  <p align="left"><strong>Amnesty Freedom Challenge</strong><br>    
    We have all received information from Gus asking us to bring to the Gathering ideas of what we will do locally for Freedom week. You should also have received an information pack direct from Amnesty...to us as Incedo....with some good information and asking us to fill in a form with our ideas and goals for Freedom week. This form is due in by Monday 14th May. Please get this to them. This is the first Incedo 'contact' with another group....lets do it right! If you have questions contact Gus <a href="mailto:g.row@yfc.org.nz">g.row@yfc.org.nz</a> </p>
